{"tid":327112,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"災難藝術家預告：一套有關史上最爛電影的電影","createTime":"2017-07-18T13:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T07:45:17.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5cf844ae38e3d7ee0ab1792ef802696891adcca","tid":327112,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pTdZrsQilVY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpTdZrsQilVY&d=aQt1QW1FEZ4rDijKz7O32PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=276c5763\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pTdZrsQilVY</a><br />\n<br />\nOh<br />\nHi<br />\nMark"},{"pid":"729c309b8b4aca42b96391d9389eedd26d373ba8","tid":327112,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:53:06.000Z","msg":"今年台灣出了一部話題度超高的「爛片」《台北物語》，因為實在太過獵奇反而造成了一股搶看風潮，不過時間回到 2003 年，美國也有一部因為真的太難看反而受到熱烈歡迎的作品《房間》（The Room），而片中主要演員為此撰寫了一本著作〈災難藝術家〉（The Disaster Artist: My Life Inside the Room）描述拍攝的背後故事，這個有趣的題材被同樣有著藝術家之心的詹姆斯法蘭柯看到，為此改編了一部電影《災難藝術家》（The Disaster Artist）首支前導預告也上線了，同時相信也會馬上惹怒你。<br />\n<br />\n預告中看到留著長髮同時也是《房間》編劇、導演、男主角的湯姆比賽爾（Tom Bissell）在綠幕前面因為一句再簡單不過的台詞而 NG 了數十遍，最後講出來的語調、節奏也都詭異不行，最厲害的最終也收錄於正片裡面，本片也將敘述另一位演員桂葛賽斯泰瑞歐（Greg Sestero）在整個拍攝過程中的故事以及該片的「爛」口碑所造成的影響。<br />\n<br />\n演出卡司除了詹姆斯法蘭科親自飾演湯米維索外，還找來了弟弟及准弟媳：戴夫法蘭科（Dave Franco）與艾莉森布利（Alison Brie）、好友：賽斯羅根（Seth Rogen）與布萊恩克萊斯頓（Bryan Cranston）、柔伊德區（Zoey Deutch）、柴克艾弗隆（Zac Efron）、喬許哈契森（Josh Hutcherson）、莎朗史東（Sharon Stone）、克里斯多福米茲布拉斯（Christopher Mintz-Plasse）等。"},{"pid":"6feac68d8f39e694afd5d94267dce9647bca870c","tid":327112,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:54:38.000Z","msg":"好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cb0144ef6c8e65219093b402c3c6ac78139a91","tid":327112,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c009f2ccd9b7d63578f47a8a44c8c5c0654dbe7","tid":327112,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚正"},{"pid":"246d46b782342c4ee27036914b9198dd5b0afcf0","tid":327112,"uid":40306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/bTvKRBBaMmb04/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FbTvKRBBaMmb04%2Fgiphy.gif&h=78bae2f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abc6e763c670c00522fe88bb32a80c6b36219bc0","tid":327112,"uid":63233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:02:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"237854b70c086e7c815bfa8cacb3e902accca389","tid":327112,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/bTvKRBBaMmb04/giphy.gif&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FbTvKRBBaMmb04%2Fgiphy.gif%22&d=aQt1QW1FEZ4rDijKz7O32PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=21c509a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://media.giphy.com/media/bTvKRBBaMmb04/giphy.gif&quot;</a>  /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://33.media.tumblr.com/1abe3e8c18262f9047bddc30010fc53a/tumblr_naxll2gzDw1rskk8io5_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F33.media.tumblr.com%2F1abe3e8c18262f9047bddc30010fc53a%2Ftumblr_naxll2gzDw1rskk8io5_400.gif&h=a3bacc69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1abdefbcd738882be74850131b9e3f575bbc6c4e","tid":327112,"uid":4758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會一路睇一路鬧但又停唔到"},{"pid